org.pvg.plasmagraph.models

Class GraphModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pvg.plasmagraph.models.GraphModel

  • public class GraphModel
extends Object

    Model Class for the Graph window's MVC.

    Handles the calling of classes when the Graph button has been pressed.

    Author:
    Plasma Visualization Group

      • graph

        public org.jfree.chart.JFreeChart graph()

        Graphs the columns specified in GraphPair p with data in DataSet ds according to the settings in Template t. Uses JFreeChart to create the appropriate graph!

        Returns:
        A JFreeChart object containing an XYGraph or a BarGraph to display.

      • unscannedGraphing

        public Graph unscannedGraphing()

        Graphs the columns specified in GraphPair p with data in DataSet ds according to the settings in Template t. Uses JFreeChart to create the appropriate graph! Does not scan the data for outliers before other functions.

        Parameters:
        interpolation_switch -

      • scannedGraphing

        public Graph scannedGraphing()

        Graphs the columns specified in GraphPair p with data in DataSet ds according to the settings in Template t. Uses JFreeChart to create the appropriate graph! Scans the data for outliers before other functions.

        Parameters:
        interpolation_switch -
